Add `date` or `TP` class to a text input to enable the date picker:

~~~ .html
<input type="text" class="date" value="2017/14/14 13:00:22">
~~~

Or use `date` type in the Panel API:

~~~ .php
return [
    'type' => 'date',
    'value' => time()
];
~~~

*[API]: Application Programming Interface